Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.01,0:01:34.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.47,0:01:37.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.71,0:01:40.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事 問題無
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.18,0:01:43.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們的嘉依卡怎樣了?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.35,0:01:45.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.92,0:01:46.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.03,0:01:49.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 那趕緊開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.39,0:01:51.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.21,0:01:55.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,順便一提 若交換人質時我們遭到狙擊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.70,0:01:57.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或踩到陷阱 我就會拉動這根繩子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.70,0:02:01.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它會引燃炸藥 炸飛我們週遭一帶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.34,0:02:02.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.01,0:02:05.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 故弄玄虛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.34,0:02:08.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那豈不是你們也得同歸於盡…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.17,0:02:09.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是亂破師的戰法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.46,0:02:17.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想保證首先人質成功交換 其它容後再說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.27,0:02:19.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.79,0:02:22.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對方也是毫不疏忽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.95,0:02:23.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還挺棘手的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.66,0:02:26.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧 小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.50,0:02:30.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.94,0:02:43.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅與白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.93,0:02:55.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.32,0:03:00.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇眼鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.40,0:03:01.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這數量可麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.12,0:03:12.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂喂 怎麼回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.49,0:03:13.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還好吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.05,0:03:19.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這幫傢伙應該沒有結群的習性
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.71,0:03:20.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被操縱了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.17,0:03:21.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.30,0:03:28.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魚自己跳到地上?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.50,0:03:33.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我互換了在水中與空氣中的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.55,0:03:38.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若多項知覺失常 任何生物都不能安然無恙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.21,0:03:43.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這招的好處在於 不用擔心因魔法本身而誤殺對方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.87,0:03:46.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正適合用於活捉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.53,0:03:48.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 真是令我吃了一驚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.68,0:03:50.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到來了兩個嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.34,0:03:53.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求之不得的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.68,0:03:57.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都抓回去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.83,0:04:05.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.95,0:04:07.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碰到光線就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.79,0:04:09.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要回頭 快點跑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.48,0:04:18.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用魔法遮掩視線嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.57,0:04:20.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們也動手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.43,0:04:25.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋 不還是虛張聲勢嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.56,0:04:29.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 這次有人礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.29,0:04:31.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交換暫時中止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.36,0:04:33.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.62,0:04:34.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.80,0:04:35.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此地 不宜久留
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.25,0:04:42.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去追那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.53,0:04:43.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:45.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種時候 魔法真是方便
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.44,0:04:48.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們只能殺出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:49.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.44,0:04:50.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武器 返還
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.20,0:04:52.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.23,0:04:56.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.20,0:04:58.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼下挨過此劫為先
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.13,0:04:59.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.30,0:05:02.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.48,0:05:50.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦? 你們怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.99,0:05:54.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像很累的樣子?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.96,0:05:55.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.18,0:06:00.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡 你換了髮型?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.34,0:06:03.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呀…這傢伙看起像平常的嘉依卡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.58,0:06:06.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是嗎 那是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.22,0:06:09.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 雖然也是嘉依卡啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.47,0:06:11.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之 以後再和你說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.41,0:06:14.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前 問題是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.69,0:06:17.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但兄長 即使挪開了瓦礫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.45,0:06:18.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們中也沒有能駕駛的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.29,0:06:20.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.34,0:06:22.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而再磨蹭下去就要被追上了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.35,0:06:24.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能丟在這裡了呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.29,0:06:26.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼 要開動這機車?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.35,0:06:28.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我幫你開嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.97,0:06:30.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能用魔法的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.93,0:06:31.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你來?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.95,0:06:33.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你願意之後和我打一場
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.42,0:06:36.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了 趕緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.47,0:06:37.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.68,0:06:49.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裝鎧龍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.63,0:06:58.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣根本無從追跡…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.42,0:07:05.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬特烏斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.65,0:07:06.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我失手了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.93,0:07:10.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到這麼多棄獸竟能全部殺光
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.11,0:07:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是失算了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.94,0:07:15.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這邊也是 所有線索都被破壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.50,0:07:20.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來單靠我們兩人同時抓捕兩組嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.48,0:07:21.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終究是太托大了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.25,0:07:24.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩名嘉依卡聚在一起究竟是想做什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.69,0:07:28.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過她們中是否有真身都還是未知之數
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.07,0:07:32.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許反過來 其實都是真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:34.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.15,0:07:38.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然是皇帝 那妻妾如雲一點都不奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.22,0:07:41.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許他為了萬無一失地培養出繼承人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.53,0:07:45.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給生下來的所有女兒都取了嘉依卡這個名字…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.29,0:07:49.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說所有的嘉依卡都是真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.28,0:07:51.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.84,0:07:55.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說到底我們對嘉依卡一無所知
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.70,0:07:57.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.28,0:08:01.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那更應該全都抓獲進行尋問了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.63,0:08:06.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在我們只能寄希望於前往佩利梅拉爾的本隊了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.87,0:08:16.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 繞路走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.24,0:08:21.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六國會議期間 此路禁止通行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.89,0:08:25.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關於此前大戰中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.25,0:08:30.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迫降於加瓦爾尼公爵領的航天要塞索厄拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.74,0:08:36.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據悉公爵動用了大量的化石思念料 擅自將要塞起動了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.93,0:08:38.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目的不明
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.97,0:08:43.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需立即遣使者問明公爵真意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.07,0:08:44.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太過溫和!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.93,0:08:48.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟將處於聯合國管理下的航天要塞私有化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.90,0:08:50.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反意昭然若揭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.12,0:08:54.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對待逆賊 唯有以武力肅清!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.24,0:08:55.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫急莫急
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.78,0:08:59.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先還是探探對方的態度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.78,0:09:00.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起此事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.98,0:09:06.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近我國農民圍繞農地劃分問題紛爭不斷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.78,0:09:09.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還請借助聯軍之力 予以鎮壓…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.51,0:09:10.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,農民的小衝突算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.18,0:09:11.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起這種問題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.45,0:09:13.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是先處理下在我國橫行霸道的強盜團夥…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.52,0:09:15.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 我國的貧窮問題…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.64,0:09:16.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肅靜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.06,0:09:20.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請舉手後再發言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.13,0:09:25.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有何事? 斯坦梅茨大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.13,0:09:30.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關於我克里曼機關正追蹤調查的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.54,0:09:32.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「棺姬嘉依卡」一事…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.88,0:09:34.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.95,0:09:38.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種民間傳說的報告 聽了純屬浪費時間
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.15,0:09:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 現在追蹤的嘉依卡 實際入手了數樣遺體
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.56,0:09:46.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其為真身的可信度…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.18,0:09:46.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笑掉大牙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.03,0:09:48.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起這種天方夜譚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.44,0:09:52.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還不如去調停下方才講到的農民衝突
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.01,0:09:55.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這才是戰後復興機關的分內之事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.11,0:10:00.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實 此事想來正適合克里曼機關出面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.50,0:10:02.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,諸位怎看?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.88,0:10:07.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若命令如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.10,0:10:12.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼? 去鎮壓農村?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.81,0:10:14.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但根據馬特烏斯的報告
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.13,0:10:17.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡一行人已近在咫尺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.05,0:10:19.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都到了這一步 怎可輕易…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.47,0:10:20.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的心情我可以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.23,0:10:24.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但六國會議的決定不容違逆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.53,0:10:25.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請立刻動身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.01,0:10:30.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.27,0:10:33.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.46,0:11:01.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 亂破師?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.40,0:11:01.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.49,0:11:03.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.57,0:11:06.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僱主 我的假貨?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.21,0:11:10.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說過 現在誰真誰假還說不准呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.17,0:11:13.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,報酬金額 提出
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.39,0:11:15.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更多 我支付
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.86,0:11:18.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遲早復興 賈茲帝國
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.63,0:11:20.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,報酬 如你所願
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.90,0:11:22.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要我為金錢而叛主?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.87,0:11:27.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 亂破師為了金錢 可以受僱於任何勢力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.86,0:11:29.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.04,0:11:32.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦選定了僱主就絕不會背叛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.53,0:11:35.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我們唯一的驕傲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.77,0:11:38.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.21,0:11:40.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使命 絕對
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.54,0:11:42.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使耗費一生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.74,0:11:44.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也要努力完成
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.66,0:11:49.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有戰場戰鬥才是亂破師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.18,0:11:52.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不止是為了錢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.71,0:11:55.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 戰場 提供 可能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.31,0:11:57.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能當你的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.72,0:11:58.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我說過…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.77,0:12:00.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 力量 需要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.77,0:12:02.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰鬥 奪回
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.66,0:12:03.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路之所往 戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.38,0:12:05.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迷茫 搖擺 沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.44,0:12:13.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該準備做飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.98,0:12:15.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考慮 提議
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.90,0:12:17.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我會考慮的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.63,0:12:43.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.72,0:12:45.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要買件武器嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.37,0:12:47.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這品種齊全哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.42,0:12:50.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就知道能遇上你們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.98,0:12:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟這附近只有這一個大城市
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.82,0:12:57.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡平安無事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.62,0:12:58.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.27,0:13:01.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也有人質在你那兒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.02,0:13:11.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在猶豫?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.41,0:13:13.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猶豫什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.46,0:13:15.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猶豫追隨哪邊的嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.74,0:13:16.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你聽到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.26,0:13:19.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托魯啊 你以前說過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.63,0:13:23.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,實現重要之人的目的 就是自己的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.94,0:13:25.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那指的是嘉依卡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.43,0:13:27.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.43,0:13:30.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是渴望戰鬥所以才受僱於嘉依卡吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.00,0:13:34.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那轉到紅嘉依卡那邊不也一樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.08,0:13:37.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仔細想想 其實投靠紅嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.71,0:13:40.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托魯更能盡情戰鬥吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.04,0:13:41.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這麼想?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.28,0:13:42.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.57,0:13:45.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.82,0:13:46.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 阿卡莉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.83,0:13:49.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了 兄長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.85,0:13:51.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 有收獲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.67,0:13:54.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有 交換的安排定下了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.22,0:13:58.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天黃昏 佩利梅拉爾中央廣場
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.88,0:14:00.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.13,0:14:02.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也去告知她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.61,0:14:06.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托魯會選哪邊呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.00,0:14:14.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時間地點談好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.01,0:14:17.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你馬上可以回到那倆亂破師身邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.73,0:14:19.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.01,0:14:21.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唔 反倒被感謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.85,0:14:32.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提議
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.53,0:14:36.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提議 考慮 換主
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.32,0:14:38.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.73,0:14:41.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對我 不滿?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.17,0:14:45.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有不滿 復興帝國和復仇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.21,0:14:48.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想必在目標明確的你的麾下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.06,0:14:51.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我更能盡情地戰鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.52,0:14:53.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.34,0:14:55.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.55,0:14:58.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論精神還是肉體
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.52,0:15:01.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.95,0:15:04.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻是個爛好人 全身上下都是可乘之隙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.03,0:15:06.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且還老實又固執
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.91,0:15:09.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令人放心不下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.52,0:15:12.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然都是被需要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.38,0:15:15.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想效力於更需要我的一方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.33,0:15:18.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這麼回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.74,0:15:20.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.59,0:15:23.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又何嘗不…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.73,0:15:28.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.46,0:15:31.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.13,0:15:34.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不叫大叔 叫達比特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.91,0:15:35.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,達比特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.80,0:15:47.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.58,0:16:05.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托魯 阿卡莉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.30,0:16:06.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.06,0:16:08.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.35,0:16:11.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.52,0:16:14.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托魯 反應淡薄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.14,0:16:17.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難不成我還得喜極而泣?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.97,0:16:19.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你饒了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.39,0:16:22.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.71,0:16:25.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這時最為鬆懈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.57,0:16:29.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托魯其實挺擔心嘉依卡的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.57,0:16:31.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,詳細希望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.94,0:16:34.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他保養武器保養個不停
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.72,0:16:37.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道的 托魯總是不坦率嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.04,0:16:40.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼說來著 怕羞?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.62,0:16:42.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理解 大大理解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.79,0:16:45.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 模仿就不能把口吻也模仿了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.22,0:16:49.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是阿卡莉的說話方式太難了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.72,0:16:56.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,致盲者 顯現
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.62,0:17:16.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.01,0:17:18.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才那是什麼? 魔法?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.87,0:17:19.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.14,0:17:20.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁現在 我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.43,0:17:21.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.13,0:17:24.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,賽爾瑪那傢伙 失敗了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.22,0:17:26.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.02,0:17:30.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小嘉依卡 你不會被人家迷住了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.60,0:17:34.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,粗俗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.15,0:17:45.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕快離開這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.92,0:17:48.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉嘉依卡 還得請你馬上去開車
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.07,0:17:52.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果托魯還是選了白嘉依卡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.34,0:17:55.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.14,0:17:57.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說明 請求
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.56,0:17:58.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.60,0:18:00.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那啥 怕羞啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.04,0:18:02.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怕羞你個頭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.64,0:18:06.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.31,0:18:07.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿卡莉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.73,0:18:17.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿卡莉 感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.74,0:18:21.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎回來 嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.11,0:18:29.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托魯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.40,0:18:31.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.71,0:18:34.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 嘉依卡·托勒龐特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.79,0:18:37.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡 有許多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.78,0:18:39.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.76,0:18:43.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 記憶 缺落
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.19,0:18:45.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假貨 可能性…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.58,0:18:47.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.47,0:18:50.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最初遇到的嘉依卡是你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.29,0:18:53.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想侍奉的嘉依卡也是你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.69,0:18:55.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不就夠了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.33,0:19:03.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我會毫不猶豫地掃清你前路的一切障礙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.20,0:19:07.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論對方是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.47,0:19:18.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我重申一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.39,0:19:20.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交出遺體
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.98,0:19:21.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.26,0:19:23.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.38,0:19:26.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知為何 咱們的大小姐對你是青睞有加
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.84,0:19:31.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若你帶著遺體加入我們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.05,0:19:33.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就可以避免無用的爭鬥喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.96,0:19:38.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再加上你妹妹 聽說還有頭裝鎧龍?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.56,0:19:40.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她說一起來也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.77,0:19:43.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若照做 我這邊的公主 你們打算如何處置?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.39,0:19:47.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡 不需兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.93,0:19:49.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.72,0:19:51.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.41,0:19:52.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是你們的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.58,0:20:09.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開膛者 顯現
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.05,0:20:21.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托魯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.21,0:20:23.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托魯不要動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.72,0:20:28.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閃爍者 顯現吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.83,0:20:29.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The Flasher
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.39,0:20:37.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,障眼法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.67,0:20:39.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我為鋼也
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.58,0:20:43.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鋼故不怯 鋼故不惑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.39,0:20:47.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦逢敵 盡無一切躊躇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.03,0:20:49.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為滅此兇器也
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.41,0:20:51.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鐵血轉化
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.54,0:21:09.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄長
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.53,0:21:10.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.57,0:21:11.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不成 被逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.61,0:21:13.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法師那邊呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.84,0:21:14.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這邊也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.95,0:21:16.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托魯 阿卡莉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.78,0:21:20.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事? 兩人沒問題?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.56,0:21:28.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能這樣下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.50,0:21:32.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不僅有人妨礙收集遺體
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.40,0:21:36.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至還有人想搶奪我們收集的遺體
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.24,0:21:38.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來該怎麼走…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.11,0:21:40.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得好好想一想了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.14,0:21:47.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡 複數 不需
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.53,0:21:49.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遲早 做了結
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.39,0:21:53.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.79,0:23:29.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怕山谷 訪問者 無人歸來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.72,0:23:31.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或某處 遺體存在?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.06,0:23:35.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此必須訪問 絕對生還
